https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/f8nus5CdHnUk17wSNccQ9la3w52.jpg The Crane Chorus and Crane Symphony Orchestra of the State University of New York at Potsdam present a holiday concert conducted by Daniel Gordon and Christopher Lanz. The Christmas and seasonal selections include "O Come All Ye Faithful," "Deck the Halls," "Christmas Day: A Choral Fantasy on Old Carols," "The First Noel," "Hanukkah Festival Overture," and "Hark, the Herald Angels Sing."
